  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients presenting for elective surgery requiring orotracheal intubation will be randomized
      to being intubated with either the conventional (reusable) GlideScope videolaryngoscope or
      the single-use GlideScope videolaryngoscope. The primary outcome is time to intubation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
